  Scalr-tools is a command-line interface to your Scalr account

  Version 2.0 is intended to work with the new Scalr JSON API. 

Install:
  $ git clone https://github.com/Scalr/pecha.git
  $ cd pecha/
  $ git checkout develop
  $ pip install --editable .
  $ . scalr-tools-complete.sh 
  
Configure:
  TBD
  
Use:
  
  $ scalr-tools --help
  $ scalr-tools <tab> <tab>
